{"id":938227359,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"3 weeks, 1 day","timestamp":1682222309,"status":14,"status_display":"Time Limit Exceeded","runtime":"N/A","url":"/submissions/detail/938227359/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Sliding Subarray Beauty","memory":"N/A","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    \n    int numOfNeg(vector<int> nums){\n        int count = 0;\n        for(int num:nums){\n            if(num<0) count++;\n        }\n        return count;\n    }\n    \n    vector<int> getSubarrayBeauty(vector<int>& nums, int k, int x) {\n        vector<int> ans;\n        int i=0;\n        int j=0;\n        int n = nums.size();\n        int count = 0;\n        vector<int> temp;\n        while(j<=n && i<n){\n            if(j-i+1>k){\n                vector<int> copy(temp);\n                i++;\n                if(numOfNeg(temp)<x){\n                    ans.push_back(0);\n                }\n                else{\n                    sort(temp.begin(), temp.end());\n                    ans.push_back(*(temp.begin()+x-1));\n                }\n                copy.erase(copy.begin(), copy.begin()+1);\n                temp = copy;\n            }\n            if(j<n)\n            temp.push_back(nums[j]);\n            j++;\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"sliding-subarray-beauty","has_notes":false}
